Introduction: An acoustic piano, keyboard, stringed percussion instrument in which the strings are struck by wooden hammers that are coated with a softer material.
SuitablFor: Musicians who entertain audiences with piano music. They may perform in front of live audiences in theatre productions, supermarkets, and hotels, or work in a studio.
